# setvl

SVL-Form

* setvl RT, RA, SVi, vs, ms
* setvl. RT, RA, SVi, vs, ms

Pseudo-code:

    VLimm <- SVi + 1
    if vs = 1 then
        if RA = 0 then
            VL <- (RA)[57:63]
        else
            VL <- VLimm[2:8]
    else
        VL <- SVSTATE[7:13]
    if ms = 1 then
        MVL <- VLimm[2:8]
    else
        MVL <- SVSTATE[0:6]
    if VL > MVL then
        VL = MVL
    SVSTATE[0:6] = MVL
    SVSTATE[7:13] = VL
    if RT != 0 then
        RT <- VL || [0] * 58

Special Registers Altered:

    CR0                     (if Rc=1)

